2010-05-20 04:50:00
  Added secondlife 1.23.5.136274 ebuild. Based it off coolvlviewer due to set up for 1.23.5 code.
  Now use secondlife.eclass

2009-08-09 17:58:41
  Added Click Action Buy beacons to secondlife
  Added to secondlife and snowglobe-trunk:
    Audio beconds color by Aleric
    Long audio times bugfix by Aleric
    Drop down avatar list on login screen by Cypren
  Reworked the install.xml file live pull and now cache with md5sum check on snowglobe-trunk. Will propergate it out to other svn builds.

2009-07-03 00:08:40
  fixed homesite URL for GreenLife
  Screw the changelog format, the ebuilds will never get in portage.
  Fix bug in 1.22.11.113941-r8, dos2unix was not done before crash to core option patch.
  Stuff I did earler and never got around to updateing the changelog
  Added sometime ago, 1.23.4.124025. Debated on masking or not due to this verison was rushed out the door. Dessided not to.
  Remove cool and restrainedlife USE flags, going to do a seperate coolsl ebuild.
  added GreenLife, Hippo, Imprudence, snowglobe, and snowglobe ebuilds to the overlay. Need to check for overlay changelog.
  Remove some stale secondlife svn builds to help maintaining overlay easer. Also remove a bunch of earler ebuilds from all branches.
  Patch tut with skip_test so snowglobe ebuilds can now build with unit tests. USE test flag change to unit_test, some systems masked test USE flag.

